00:02:15.357 --> 00:02:18.706
and start a practice or go into an HMO now.

58
00:02:18.706 --> 00:02:21.692
<v ->So I'm going to paint you a very broad picture of that.</v>

59
00:02:21.692 --> 00:02:23.890
The first piece, getting into practice,

60
00:02:23.890 --> 00:02:28.890
the average medical school graduate has a $180,000 debt.

61
00:02:28.916 --> 00:02:31.069
They're, generally speaking, in their late 20s

