00:03:19.248 --> 00:03:20.997
may be offended by that statement,

82
00:03:20.997 --> 00:03:23.365
because doctors are not repairing cars,

83
00:03:23.365 --> 00:03:25.520
but we're working in a gray zone,

84
00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:27.397
where you often don't know what's going on.

85
00:03:27.397 --> 00:03:29.496
You have an inkling of what the diagnosis might be

86
00:03:29.496 --> 00:03:31.002
or what the treatment might be,

87
