or there may be 10 or 20 different potential treatments

88
00:03:33.180 --> 00:03:34.460
for any health cause.

89
00:03:34.460 --> 00:03:38.086
So the decision process is not just black and white,

90
00:03:38.086 --> 00:03:41.527
and yet you're judged on that basis, okay?

91
00:03:41.527 --> 00:03:44.514
So you have that, you have the financial pressures,

92
00:03:44.514 --> 00:03:46.291
the pressures of generally starting a family

