00:03:48.146 --> 00:03:50.173
and then you're stuck in most environments

95
00:03:50.173 --> 00:03:52.910
wth anywhere from a 10 to 15 minute office visit,

96
00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:56.665
which no physician would find appropriate or reasonable.

97
00:03:56.665 --> 00:03:59.673
It's the pressure of the employer in that case,

98
00:03:59.673 --> 00:04:02.969
because frankly, most docs are now employed,

99
00:04:02.969 --> 00:04:04.367
the pressure of the employer

