00:04:08.463 --> 00:04:12.196
is faced with a plethora of stresses and pressures,

103
00:04:12.196 --> 00:04:14.628
and it's very, very difficult for them to get started.

104
00:04:14.628 --> 00:04:16.441
<v Regina>Let's pick up on a thread you were talking about</v>

