00:05:01.326 --> 00:05:04.035
"Do I feel motivated to make change in my life

126
00:05:04.035 --> 00:05:07.560
because of this person that I was with, this physician?"

127
00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:11.224
So paper performance and the physician-patient relationship

128
00:05:11.224 --> 00:05:13.506
sometimes are actually at odds.

129
00:05:13.506 --> 00:05:14.659
<v Regina>Yeah, that makes total sense.</v>

