00:05:16.328 --> 00:05:20.190
and bring a particular stat theyr'e looking for down,

132
00:05:20.190 --> 00:05:22.259
but that doesn't mean you've got a relationship

133
00:05:22.259 --> 00:05:23.999
and maybe even a healthy lifestyle shift

134
00:05:23.999 --> 00:05:24.989
with the patient, right?

135
00:05:24.989 --> 00:05:26.516
<v ->Right, so the end product for the patient</v>

