00:05:43.445 --> 00:05:45.323
may not even be appropriate numbers.

145
00:05:45.323 --> 00:05:49.739
They're just general numbers based on populations.

146
00:05:49.739 --> 00:05:52.725
So for the individual, they may actually have no relevance.

147
00:05:52.725 --> 00:05:55.605
So the physician is up against all of these issues.

148
00:05:55.605 --> 00:05:58.869
How they're measured, the time pressures,

149
00:05:58.869 --> 00:06:01.664
the performance pressures,

150
00:06:01.664 --> 00:06:04.225
and it makes it a very difficult situation

